for O(1) lookup; convert to list only when adding to solvents[] audit 
metadata or _dup_warnings.

In parse_composition_footnotes(): return matched_entries as list of dicts; 
never expose the internal seen_markers set.

LAYER 3 (payload boundary sanitizer) — Optional defensive walker.

Add to each workflow's payload builder as final step before returning:

def _sanitize_payload(obj):
if isinstance(obj, (set, frozenset)):
return sorted(list(obj), key=str)
if isinstance(obj, dict):
return {k: _sanitize_payload(v) for k, v in obj.items()}
if isinstance(obj, list):
return [_sanitize_payload(v) for v in obj]
if isinstance(obj, tuple):
return [_sanitize_payload(v) for v in obj]
return obj

payload = _sanitize_payload(payload)
return payload

Cheap insurance. Runs once per generation. Catches anything missed at Layer 2.

